summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5870 for the improvement of 29th Avenue Southwest, from West Holden Street to West Myrtle Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 77304, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
